{"tid":60171,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「他知道，哭是沒有用的。」","createTime":"2016-12-30T08:43:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-21T12:19:53.000Z","uid":28938,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f3f0aa9f5fb8f04b769d673a977ec1a307e62522","tid":60171,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:43:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/30/164318_18923fd920df0e757ac5e4651a5dba5f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F30%2F164318_18923fd920df0e757ac5e4651a5dba5f.jpg&h=f91b5ca8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「他知道，哭是沒有用的。」 <br />\n<br />\nC朗拿度為父還債，所以17歲出道，開始了自己的足球生涯。C朗踢的第一家球會士砵亭，有一次打呲大戰他獨力和對方整條後防線廝殺，因為太過投入，他不小心踢到了門柱，腳立即受傷，血如泉湧。 <br />\n<br />\n球證立刻喊停，要送他去醫院。但C朗知道，這一去醫院，勢必要換人，那他的「球星之途」也許從此就斷了。於是，17歲的他對領隊說：「找來這麼多球迷捧場不容易，我能堅持。」<br />\n<br />\n於是，他將酒精直接倒在傷口上，再將膠袋包著腳，穿上球鞋繼續比賽。換了四個膠袋，倒出四袋血，同時亦攻進對方兩球。球場完時，他幾乎暈倒。 <br />\n<br />\n送到醫院，醫生說，再遲來一點，人就玩完了，而且，極有可能得到破傷風。<br />\n<br />\n在給他縫針之前，醫生讓他簽生死狀。 縫針時，C朗就那麼看著，不喊、不叫、不哭，沒有打麻醉針，就那樣一針一針地縫著。一個17歲的少年，知道自己面對的是怎樣的人生。<br />\n<br />\n「他知道，哭是沒有用的。 」<br />\n<br />\n最後一針，C朗對醫生說：「我來縫！」醫生看著他，他居然笑了︰「沒有嘗試過的人生，我都想嘗試一下。」 <br />\n<br />\n這句話多麼豪邁，在場的人震驚了。因為醫生說，如果熬不過去，他也只有四天的生命了，所以，他願意嘗試生命中不曾嘗試的痛，他要給自己縫一針。 <br />\n<br />\n從給自己縫針那一天開始，他知道，所有的明天全要靠自己。後來，他一直努力，不停地得獎，終於成為比美斯更名副其實的世界球皇。"},{"pid":"f4a3d30b1f82196729d3c39ad8db3b4cb02791d3","tid":60171,"uid":14872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:57:10.000Z","msg":"禾朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad272b6e54494426c09667d1f4b15fd4e5249a19","tid":60171,"uid":19978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T09:12:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9756d35661e60ea1b756b7de17cd01c802ad14d","tid":60171,"uid":1289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T09:13:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29567ee81d02051b94c088298ed853531226ba0a","tid":60171,"uid":15,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T09:14:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc9d5e593e6539d073b735547a9bc8c8097ca8f3","tid":60171,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T09:24:43.000Z","msg":"流哂血點可以繼續踢波呀，一睇就知吹水啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb86a1410f113b47eb97d40a632f05012f49cf34","tid":60171,"uid":61082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T09:31:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e19168f45e48cefb59ed7252ce9665cd0488d543","tid":60171,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T09:32:33.000Z","msg":"留名睇留名睇新會然既on9仔"},{"pid":"b47a08bca16308da03fad43f2b4e94a2fc3cfd1b","tid":60171,"uid":70596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T09:36:45.000Z","msg":"好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fbd489a056ced539a6292bf48f27255d241bbd3","tid":60171,"uid":24485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T09:40:31.000Z","msg":"他知道"},{"pid":"a929f85a77d3d95c1a77d0b9fe0813bec30a957e","tid":60171,"uid":24485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T09:41:10.000Z","msg":"踢波唔踢到流晒血咁踢黎把撚呀？"},{"pid":"fad92a09cf5a6fcf2843652f9213ce3bce196c4f","tid":60171,"uid":40650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T09:41:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>流哂血點可以繼續踢波呀，一睇就知吹水啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e69d5e6f29e1b8e48440f626f2a615cf9d4e4723","tid":60171,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime